name: "xapi-consts"
version: "master"
synopsis: "The xapi toolstack daemon which implements the XenAPI"
description: """
This daemon exposes the XenAPI and is used by clients such as 'xe'
and 'XenCenter' to manage clusters of Xen-enabled hosts."""
